e users’ galleries using one-step synchronization with any Squarespace account, and saves high-resolution images locally so users can showcase their work without relying on an internet connection. Portfolio also features simple display options for a variety of media styles – users can configure borders, image shapes, alignment, background shade, and more. Tapping and holding an image in the gallery view also lets users easily email images directly from the app.</p><p>Squarespace Portfolio is now available for free in the Apple App Store, and works with the iPhone and iPad. More information can be found at <a href="http://www.squarespace.com/apps#portfolio">www.squarespace.com/apps#portfolio</a>.</p><h3><strong>About Squarespace</strong></h3><p>Squarespace is a state-of-the-art website creation platform with breakthrough features that make innovative web design more accessible to the public than ever before. Since 2004, the platform has empowered millions to create and maintain modern, high-quality websites regardless of technical ability. The company’s reliable and scalable cloud infrastructure eliminates security updates, downtime, and infrastructure costs. All Squarespace customers receive award-winning, 24/7 customer support. Squarespace’s team of 107 is headquartered in downtown New York City.</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>